6 The Sentinel Chain Token Features (SENC) 
 
We intend to issue the Sentinel Chain Token (SENC), which is primarily used as 
a medium of exchange for the Local Community Token (LCT) which is then 
used to make payments for services or participate in projects. These features will 
be explained in greater detail as follows: 

 

