Payment Protocol 
 
Payment or collections protocol similar to BIP703 can be implemented using the 
atomic exchange of payment request and LCT. The payment request is implemented 
with payment details containing the merchant’s identity, and contains the PKI 
certificate and digital signature along with payment receipt information. This 
information is stored as meta-data on the blockchain and associated with the 
completed transaction as part of the atomic asset exchange. 
 

